# Project Structure & Architecture

*See @ARCHITECT for architecture and design pattern decisions.*

**See `docs/CONTEXT.md` Section 2 for complete structure details.**

## Project Structure (Canonical)

```text
src/
├── main.py                # FastAPI app entrypoint
├── models.py              # SQLModel DB tables
├── enums.py               # Enumeration types (UserRole, JobStatus, ApplicationStatus)
├── schemas.py             # Pydantic schemas
├── api/                   # FastAPI routers (thin)
│   ├── auth.py            # Authentication endpoints (register/login)
│   ├── admin.py           # Admin endpoints (company approval workflow)
│   ├── jobs_read.py       # Job read endpoints (GET operations)
│   └── jobs_write.py      # Job write endpoints (POST, PUT, DELETE operations)
├── services/              # Domain-specific business logic
│   ├── auth.py
│   ├── admin.py
│   ├── jobs.py
│   └── exceptions.py
├── core/                  # Cross-cutting infrastructure
│   ├── tasks.py           # Arq task definitions for async background jobs
│   ├── infrastructure/    # Pure infrastructure
│   │   ├── config.py
│   │   ├── database.py
│   │   ├── security.py
│   │   ├── limiter.py
│   │   └── dependencies.py
│   └── services/          # Infrastructure services
│       ├── email.py
│       └── storage.py
tests/                     # Mirrors source structure
├── api/                   # Integration tests
├── services/              # Unit tests for domain services
└── core/                  # Tests for infrastructure
    ├── infrastructure/    # Tests for infrastructure modules
    ├── services/          # Tests for infrastructure services
    └── test_tasks.py      # Tests for async task processing
```
